OL,6,FThe commission stopped short of
OL,7,Fcalling for full decriminalisation,
OL,8,Fsaying the long-term harms to public
OL,9,Fhealth were "not yet well understood".
OL,11,FInstead, Lord Falconer's committee
OL,12,Fcalled for "natural" ` as opposed to
OL,13,F"synthetic" ` cannabis to be moved
OL,14,Ffrom the Misuse of Drugs Act to the
OL,15,FPsychoactive Substances Act,
OL,16,Feffectively legalising possession of
OL,17,Fsmall amounts for personal use while
OL,18,Fcontinuing to prohibit importing,
OL,19,Fmanufacturing or distributing the drug.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@eO]tD@LOUtD@TO]uD@AOUuD@KO]
