OL,6,FThey also called for improved
OL,7,Faddiction services and greater
OL,8,Feducation for young people on the
OL,9,Fdangers of cannabis.
OL,11,FLord Falconer said: "Legalisation is
OL,12,Fnot the answer. The criminal justice
OL,13,Fsystem response needs to focus only on
OL,14,Fthe dealers and not the users.
OL,26,@sD@UOU
