OL,6,FLDC deputy chairwoman Janet Hills, a
OL,7,Fformer Metropolitan Police detective,
OL,8,Fsaid the report was "a driver for
OL,9,Fchange in our community" and called
OL,10,Ffor "a more balanced and compassionate
OL,11,Fapproach to policing in our city".
OL,13,FResponding to the report, Sir Sadiq
OL,14,Fsaid: "I've long been clear that we
OL,15,Fneed fresh thinking on how to reduce
OL,16,Fthe substantial harms associated with
OL,17,Fdrug-related crime in our communities.
