OL,6,F"The London Drugs Commission report
OL,7,Fmakes a compelling, evidenced-based
OL,8,Fcase for the decriminalisation of
OL,9,Fpossession of small quantities of
OL,10,Fnatural cannabis which the Government
OL,11,Fshould consider.
OL,13,F"It says that the current sentencing
OL,14,Ffor those caught in possession of
OL,15,Fnatural cannabis cannot be justified
OL,16,Fgiven its relative harm and people's
OL,17,Fexperience of the justice system.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
