OL,6,F"We must recognise that better
OL,7,Feducation, improved healthcare and
OL,8,Fmore effective, equitable policing of
OL,9,Fcannabis use are long overdue."
OL,11,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Fwill continue to work with partners
OL,13,Facross health, policing and wider
OL,14,Fpublic services to drive down drug
OL,15,Fuse, ensure more people receive timely
OL,16,Ftreatment and support, and make our
OL,17,Fstreets and communities safer.
