OL,6,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp
OL,7,Fsaid: "Possession of cannabis should
OL,8,Fnot be decriminalised like this. We
OL,9,Fhave seen some US and Canadian cities
OL,10,Fdevastated by soft policies on
OL,11,Faddictive and harmful drugs ` now
OL,12,FSadiq Khan wants to send London the
OL,13,Fsame way.
OL,15,F"Cannabis is illegal for a reason.
OL,16,FCannabis is associated with anti-
OL,17,Fsocial behaviour and heavy use can
OL,18,Flead to serious psychosis and severed
OL,19,Fmental health problems.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@AOU
