OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,F"US and Canadian cities which tried
OL,7,Fthis approach have ended up as crime-
OL,8,Fridden ghettos with stupefied addicts
OL,9,Fon the streets and law-abiding
OL,10,Fcitizens frightened to go there.
OL,12,F"Sadiq Khan is more interested in
OL,13,Fpolitically correct posturing for the
OL,14,Fbenefit of his left-wing friends than
OL,15,Fhe is making London a safe and nice
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,F"I completely oppose these plans. But
OL,19,Fwith a weak Labour Government in
OL,20,Fpower, there's no telling how they
OL,21,Fwill react. We must stop soft Sadiq."
